en_2137125_0	Elections Commissioner Mahinda Deshapriya states that measures are being taken to set up elections investigations units at district secretariat levels.
en_2137125_1	The Elections Commissioner stated that the steps will be taken according to the situation of each district.
en_2137125_2	Elections Commissioner Mahinda Deshapriya stated that the Elections Investigations Unit will be first setup at the Elections Secretariat on Thursday July 2.
en_2137125_3	He stated that the Investigations Unit will comprise of police and civil personnel. Mahinda Deshapriya added that this unit will be opened up at district elections secretariats on July 6.
en_2137125_4	The Elections Commissioner added that these units will be setup at divisional secretariat levels.  The situation that prevails in each area subsequent to the accepting of nominations will also be reviewed.
